'''Grandmother's Tears''' was a river on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]]. It was fed by the snowmelt of [[Grandfather's Shoulder]], and it led into the [[Great Downrush]].

